The '''Clarion Scholars Academy''' was an [[academy]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Daemen]]. Prior to the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], the [[Camblian Order]] sent 309 [[Youngling/Legends|younglings]] to the Academy; they [[Death/Legends|died]] when the ''[[Lark]]'' was destroyed.

